---
title: Nicoise Chicken Stew with aubergine, bell pepper and couscous
description: This speedy chicken stew is inspired by the no-frills cooking style the south of France is famous for. The technique and ingredients are simple, but the result is simply delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R12_W22_IE_IECLC15105-3_Main_high-37fb2f49.jpg
